        {
            "title": "馬鞍山迎海天池屋4,400萬腰斬價沽！ 8年狂蝕3,880萬 輸咗5間同屋苑2房",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期樓市回暖，不過豪宅市場仍錄得大幅蝕讓。馬鞍山<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"迎海\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:迎海;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/41p7PEI\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">迎海</a>2期迎海．星灣一伙頂層複式天池屋，新近以4,400萬元沽出，原業主持貨約8年巨蝕約3,880萬或47%，蝕額夠買同屋苑5間2房單位。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LKw9dI3.F8F57gaUHFC6eQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d250fec5c31f3f352b2de5012b6af0e4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"東半山肇輝臺6號天池屋7,500萬沽 內地客11年輸逾半億 夠買6間太古城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:東半山肇輝臺6號天池屋7,500萬沽 內地客11年輸逾半億 夠買6間太古城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47teLUF\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">東半山肇輝臺6號天池屋7,500萬沽 內地客11年輸逾半億 夠買6間太古城</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"「楷女郎」郭嘉文7,840萬沽九龍塘逸瓏天池屋 9年貶值2,840萬\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:「楷女郎」郭嘉文7,840萬沽九龍塘逸瓏天池屋 9年貶值2,840萬;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4bsGKX7\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「楷女郎」郭嘉文7,840萬沽九龍塘逸瓏天池屋 9年貶值2,840萬</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述成交單位為迎海．星灣第21座頂層複式B室，實用面積2,881平方呎，連1,005平方呎空中平台，其中平台更設有天際游泳池。該單位最新以4,400萬元沽出，成交呎價約15,272元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6f4c2f1c-8c00-3fa6-a19c-691303f9b332-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jHZD2TLtN5Y7KYB0GfegUg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/fd7c70e7c2939f9028c8ce53ca050eac\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從28Hse網站的單位放盤相可見，單位屬4房4套設計，連豪華裝修，向東北望壯麗海星灣景色，大廳與睡房均極為寬敞。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8t5J9CjzoDsAMKJGVTsC6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d273dfcecb6a7549b05a7f9cd2da2272\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查資料，原業主於2018年3月以8,280萬元買入單位，當時成交呎價約28,740元，持貨約8年易手，賬蝕約3,880萬元或約47%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"585\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hC.AOO0x098ugMFsteDOow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/25f528c358af4f6c5a2323873d7bbca0\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站資料，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"迎海\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:迎海;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4mvvxZx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">迎海</a>一個500呎左右的2房單位放盤價約700萬元，意味著上述單位蝕讓金額足夠買5間同屋苑2房。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">迎海位於烏溪沙路8號，鄰近港鐵烏溪沙站，由恆基兆業牽頭發展，設有5期，共21座，提供3,535個單位。根據28Hse網站資料，屋苑近期平均成交呎價約14,530 元，較3個月前升3.8%；近3個月錄得41宗二手成交，其中59%屬獲利離場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"肇輝臺6號\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:肇輝臺6號;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/肇輝臺6號-26596\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">肇輝臺6號</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"太古城\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:太古城;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/太古城-27352\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">太古城</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"九龍塘\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:九龍塘;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/九龍塘-27372\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">九龍塘</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"馬鞍山\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:馬鞍山;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/馬鞍山-27323\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">馬鞍山</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"新聞連結\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E8%BF%8E%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%A9%E6%B1%A0%E5%B1%8B4-400%E8%90%AC%E8%85%B0%E6%96%AC%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%BD-8%E5%B9%B4%E7%8B%82%E8%9D%953-880%E8%90%AC-%E8%BC%B8%E5%92%975%E9%96%93%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%912%E6%88%BF-75455\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"28Hse App\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse App;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/appdownload\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">28Hse App</a>。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E9%9E%8D%E5%B1%B1%E8%BF%8E%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%A9%E6%B1%A0%E5%B1%8B4-400%E8%90%AC%E8%85%B0%E6%96%AC%E5%83%B9%E6%B2%BD-8%E5%B9%B4%E7%8B%82%E8%9D%953-880%E8%90%AC-%E8%BC%B8%E5%92%975%E9%96%93%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%912%E6%88%BF-030342054.html",
